Value.value: The Great Forge has not seen any use in a long time, jusdging from appearances. Forges sit cold, tools are strewn haphazardly about, and a fine layer of dust has settled in over everything. Footprints leading from the entry to the back of the forge suggest there's been at least some traffic, lately.
